WEBVTT

1
00:03:55.000 --> 00:03:59.000
[WAKIZURE] To begin with,

2
00:03:59.000 --> 00:04:04.000
I am in the service of the Emperor Ichijo.

3
00:04:04.000 --> 00:04:12.000
I am known as Tachibana no Michinari.

4
00:04:12.000 --> 00:04:22.000
It so happens that his Lordship

5
00:04:22.000 --> 00:04:28.000
has this night had a portentous dream oracle.

6
00:04:28.000 --> 00:04:34.000
The Sanjo swordsmith Munechika

7
00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:43.000
must be ordered to forge a blade.

8
00:04:43.000 --> 00:04:50.000
I am on my way now to tell Munechika

9
00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:54.000
of this matter.

10
00:05:15.000 --> 00:05:25.000
[WAKIZURE] Is Munechika at home ?

11
00:05:31.000 --> 00:05:38.000
[WAKI] Who is it that has come here ?

12
00:05:38.000 --> 00:05:47.000
[WAKIZURE] I am a messenger from the Emperor.

13
00:05:47.000 --> 00:05:55.000
His Majesty has had a marvelous oracle in a dream.

14
00:05:55.000 --> 00:06:05.000
According to the oracle, you must forge a fine sword for him.

15
00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:11.000
Please comply with this order at once.

16
00:06:11.000 --> 00:06:24.000
[WAKI] While I certainly must agree to execute this imperial order, 

17
00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:33.000
as I do not have anyone to assist me,

18
00:06:33.000 --> 00:06:40.000
I do not know how I will be able to carry it out.

19
00:06:40.000 --> 00:06:46.000
[WAKIZURE] What you say sir, seems most strange.

20
00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:53.000
To hear that someone of your reputation

21
00:06:53.000 --> 00:07:00.000
does not have an appropriate assistant,

22
00:07:00.000 --> 00:07:06.000
is the most unfortunate news.

23
00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:14.000
