24
00:07:14.000 --> 00:07:23.000
without an assistant whose skills are equal to my own,

25
00:07:23.000 --> 00:07:34.000
it will not be possible to fulfill this order

26
00:07:34.000 --> 00:07:42.000
to forge an imperial blade.

27
00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:50.000
This is the answer I must give,

28
00:07:50.000 --> 00:07:56.000
though I am overcome with embarassment.

29
00:07:56.000 --> 00:08:03.000
[WAKIZURE] Even though it may be as you say,

30
00:08:03.000 --> 00:08:11.000
yet as this is the Emperor's wonderful dream oracle,

31
00:08:11.000 --> 00:08:17.000
it surely must be relied upon

32
00:08:17.000 --> 00:08:25.000
and you must quickly say

33
00:08:25.000 --> 00:08:33.000
you will accept the order.

34
00:08:33.000 --> 00:08:42.000
Let me repeat the imperial command!

35
00:08:42.000 --> 00:09:10.000
[WAKI] At this point, in any case, Munechika

36
00:09:18.000 --> 00:09:27.000
[JIUTAI] In any case, Munechika

37
00:09:27.000 --> 00:09:38.000
must here decide his course of action.

38
00:09:38.000 --> 00:09:55.000
Like the ripples beaten along a well-forged blade, his heart wavers.

39
00:09:55.000 --> 00:10:11.000
Yet, as the reign in the present age is righteous,

40
00:10:11.000 --> 00:10:20.000
a miracle may well be afforded me.

41
00:10:20.000 --> 00:10:30.000
I must place my trust only in this.

42
00:10:30.000 --> 00:10:45.000
I must place my trust only in this.

43
00:10:46.000 --> 00:10:55.000
[WAKIZURE] Hurry! make the sword.

44
00:10:55.000 --> 00:11:00.000
[WAKI] Yes! sir.

45
00:11:20.000 --> 00:11:32.000
[WAKI] This is a great task you have come to give me.

46
00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:44.000
Such a command can be carried out if I ask for divine help.

47
00:11:44.000 --> 00:11:56.000
As my family deity is Inari no Myojin,

48
00:11:56.000 --> 00:12:04.000
I will go at once to Inari,

49
00:12:04.000 --> 00:12:15.000
and pray concerning this matter.

50
00:12:18.000 --> 00:12:52.000
[SHITE] Ho there! Is that the Swordsmith of Sanjō, Munechika ?

51
00:12:52.000 --> 00:13:02.000
[WAKI] How mysterious! Here is someone who is certainly not an ordinary person.

52
00:13:02.000 --> 00:13:10.000
There is no path from the direction from which he has appeared,

53
00:13:10.000 --> 00:13:16.000
