242
00:55:55.000 --> 00:56:10.000
echoes throughout heaven and earth - How it resounds!

243
00:56:11.000 --> 00:56:17.000
[WAKI] And so the Imperial Blade is forged:

244
00:56:17.000 --> 00:56:22.000
On the face of it I strike: "Munechika, Swordsmith"!

245
00:56:22.000 --> 00:56:29.000
[SHITE] As your timely apprentice the god:

246
00:56:29.000 --> 00:56:39.000
"Little Fox", I skillfully strike on the reverse.

247
00:56:40.000 --> 00:56:50.000
[JIUTAI] Along the edge of the blade are beaten traces

248
00:56:50.000 --> 00:57:00.000
like wild clustering clouds.

249
00:57:00.000 --> 00:57:12.000
"Clustering Clouds of Heaven", it will be!

250
00:57:12.000 --> 00:57:23.000
[SHITE] First under Heaven:

251
00:57:23.000 --> 00:57:29.000
[JIUTAI] First under Heaven:

252
00:57:29.000 --> 00:57:36.000
The sword with two inscriptions!

253
00:57:36.000 --> 00:57:43.000
It will rule the land to the four seas,

254
00:57:43.000 --> 00:57:49.000
celebrate the abundance of the five staple crops.

255
00:57:49.000 --> 00:57:55.000
"I, before you, as the deity of your clan:

256
00:57:55.000 --> 00:58:02.000
the manifestation of Inari: the Little Fox,

257
00:58:02.000 --> 00:58:08.000
come to aid you in fulfilling your task.

258
00:58:08.000 --> 00:58:13.000
Now, I am done!" So saying, takes his leave.

259
00:58:13.000 --> 00:58:18.000
Once more he leaps upon the mass of clouds,

260
00:58:18.000 --> 00:58:25.000
Again, more he leaps upon the mass of clouds,

261
00:58:25.000 --> 00:58:52.000
and return to Higashiyama, the eastern mountains, the peak of Mt. Inari!